            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/handpicked/c1-vs-c8-which-corvette-would-you-buy/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " Convertible kicked off earlier this month, and one of the first – if not ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "first – C8 convertibles presented through the Corvette's R8C delivery program went to General Motors' former CEO, Dan Akerson. Akerson joined GM during its 2009 bankruptcy and was named CEO in 2010, and he was later replaced by the current CEO, Mary Barra, in 2014.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.facebook.com/corvettemuseum/posts/10157274460117441",
        "html": "<div id=\"fb-root\"></div>\n<script async=\"1\" defer=\"1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v8.0\" nonce=\"zn8Ihqg5\"></script><div class=\"fb-post\" data-href=\"https://www.facebook.com/corvettemuseum/posts/10157274460117441\" data-width=\"750\"><blockquote cite=\"https://www.facebook.com/corvettemuseum/posts/10157274460117441\" class=\"fb-xfbml-parse-ignore\"><p>On Wednesday our team had the privilege of delivering a 2020 Shadow Gray Stingray to former Chairman and CEO of General...</p>Posted by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/corvettemuseum/\">National Corvette Museum</a> on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/corvettemuseum/posts/10157274460117441\">Thursday, August 27, 2020</a></blockquote></div>",
        "metadata": {
          "author_name": "National Corvette Museum",
